{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because now, by now, by 1937, there were so many bad incidents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A neighbor was picked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said that he was-- he was giving out communist-- he made communist propaganda.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was giving out leaflets for-- to be communist, and they picked him up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whether it was true or not, I don't know, but he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People disappeared, and you didn't know where to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were afraid that they would come for us also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mainly, mainly we were all making sure that we learned a trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents said, you have to be-- you can't be just a dressmaker, you've got to be a good dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and she said-- they said the same thing to the others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother-- you can't be just an office person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You've got to do something that you can do in another country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You've got to learn something that will enable you to make money in another country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, well, at this-- at that time, there were only three of us in the house, as I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was-- that was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these were actually the preparations that they made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were always concerned with just trying to get out and making sure that they-- they weren't so concerned about-- my father was-- he was able to do most anything, being in the leather bag business.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He also said that he'll go as a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He'll-- he'll sew shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was able to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had-- he was able to do many things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said he can be a painter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He can be a wallpaper hanger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the biggest concern, not just in our house, with everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to-- there were doctors and dentists who suddenly became shoe solers.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
